The structural design (event-driven scheduler, comptime-generated CPU
dispatch tables, scanline-driven PPU) and many register-level behaviors
are derived from NanoBoyAdvance. Per the terms of GPL-3.0, the full
license text is included in the LICENSE file at the root of this
repository.

Hardware specifications referenced from GBATEK by Martin Korth
(https://problemkaputt.de/gbatek.htm).
